I am trying to collect a set of undocumented (in the manuals) commands for
Frontier.

Here is what I have already:

-  Double clicking on the zoom icon when in orbital view will zoom the
   current object all the way in.  This has the same effect as holding down
   the zoom icon for ages.

-  After using the communications icon, there are lots of places where you
   have a list of options.  You can select an option buy pressing the
   numbers on the numeric keypad.  The first option is 1 etc.  So to fix all
   the damage on your ship, you can press the following keys in order (no
   mouse-clicks): F4 (comms) KP1 (shipyard) KP2 (repairs) KP4 (fix).  You
   can hold down KP4 and it will auto-repeat, so there is no need to kill
   your mouse!


Have fun,
Phil.

